# World Wide Law — Environment Variables
#
# Most sources don't need any credentials. For those that do,
# check the source's .env.template file for required variables.
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in any values you need:
#   cp .env.example .env

# Example: Legifrance API (needed for FR/Legifrance* sources)
# LEGIFRANCE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
# LEGIFRANCE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
